                <article class="article">
                    <p class="lead">
                        In many countries, Intensive care is expanded to use hotels, sports arenas and even parking lots. Beds are urgently needed. So are ventilators, oxygen masks and many other things. As a team, we must focus on one thing and we focus on beds.
                    </p>
                    That being said, simple militray beds are generally available in large quantities. These are not suitable for hospital use because they are  :
                    <ul>
                        <li>Unable to support the patient in a sitting position</li>
